OL,3,CGlenn McCrory on the court case that
OL,4,Ccost him almost everything
OL,6,FBoxing legend Glenn McCrory opened up
OL,7,Fto Gregg Easteal about hitting 'rock
OL,8,Fbottom' after being cleared of sexual
OL,9,Fassault charges
OL,11,FFormer world boxing champion and
OL,12,Fbroadcaster Glenn McCrory has told ITV
OL,13,FNews how a court case last year cost
OL,14,Fhim almost everything including his
OL,15,Flife.
OL,17,FOriginally from Stanley, he won the
OL,18,Fcruiserweight title in 1989 before
OL,19,Fgoing on to become one of the boxing's
OL,20,Fmost respected broadcasters for 20
OL,21,Fyears.
