OL,3,CGlenn McCrory on the court case that
OL,4,Ccost him almost everything
OL,6,FBut his life took a hit more painful
OL,7,Fthan any boxing bout when he was
OL,8,Faccused of sexual assault after
OL,9,Fwaitress staff complained he had
OL,10,Fcalled them "pet" and "darling", and
OL,11,Ftouched the elbow of one of them while
OL,12,Fasking where his food was.
OL,14,FThe circumstances made headlines and
OL,15,Fraised eyebrows.
OL,17,FGlenn, 59, was quickly
OL,19,F"I was rock bottom," he told ITV Tyne
OL,20,FTees "I lost everything.
