OL,3,CGlenn McCrory on the court case that
OL,4,Ccost him almost everything
OL,6,F"Work dried up completely over the
OL,7,Flast two years with the phone not
OL,8,Fringing.
OL,10,F"And then with such an awful stigma
OL,11,Fhanging over your head, I wouldn't go
OL,12,Fout of the house. I was going for
OL,13,Fwalks at like four in the morning."
OL,15,FGlenn admits that he considered taking
OL,16,Fhis own life due to the toll it was
OL,17,Ftaking on him mentally.
