OL,3,CGlenn McCrory on the court case that
OL,4,Ccost him almost everything
OL,6,F"I wouldn't even want to try and
OL,7,Fexplain how bad it is," he said. "So
OL,8,Fmany people get there and it's a
OL,9,Fhorrible place when you try to take
OL,10,Fyour own life.
OL,12,F"And I was past that point. I'm still
OL,13,Fgetting treatment and it is a day-to-
OL,14,Fday fight just keep yourself in the
OL,15,Fright mood and to keep yourself
OL,16,Ffeeling good.
OL,18,F"You go for walks and remind yourself
OL,19,Fthat your family loves you and that
OL,20,Fsort of stuff.
