OL,3,CGlenn McCrory on the court case that
OL,4,Ccost him almost everything
OL,6,F"I really feel for people who are in
OL,7,Fthat sort of predicament where they've
OL,8,Flost everything. They haven't got a
OL,9,Fhome. They haven't got friends.
OL,11,F"I mean, I've got good people and
OL,12,Fsupport and good people around me but
OL,13,Fit doesn't matter when you are that
OL,14,Flow. You don't you don't ask, you
OL,15,Fdon't tell people.
OL,17,F"You just wallow in the sadness, the
OL,18,Fdarkness and that's a horrible place."
