OL,3,CGlenn McCrory on the court case that
OL,4,Ccost him almost everything
OL,6,FHe now hopes to use his experience to
OL,7,Ftry and help others who have lost
OL,8,Feverything, taking part in a charity
OL,9,Fsleepout at St James' Park next week
OL,10,Fto raise awareness for homelessness.
OL,12,FGlenn faced losing his home himself
OL,13,Fbut was able to stay thanks to the
OL,14,Fkindness of his landlord.
OL,16,F"Yeah it is," he said when asked if it
OL,17,Fwas now a subject close to his heart.
OL,18,F"That's why I thought I had to do this
OL,19,Fand I had to speak about it and let
OL,20,Fpeople know.
