OL,3,CGlenn McCrory on the court case that
OL,4,Ccost him almost everything
OL,6,F"People just automatically think that
OL,7,Fif you've been on TV or you've had
OL,8,Fsome success in your life, that you're
OL,9,Fokay and everything's great but that's
OL,10,Fnot the case.
OL,12,F"There are a lot of people that have
OL,13,Fdone lots of great things and had
OL,14,Fgreat jobs that are really struggling."
